JSTL: JSP Standard Tag Library
IT is a collection of custom tags that provides many functionalities to
JSP applications.

i)Iterations and Conditionals
ii)Formatting 
iii)Internationalization
iv)XML data processing
v)Database access

Advantages:
i)Fast development
ii)Code reusability
iii)No need to use scriplet tag	

JSTL Tags:
i)Core Tags: Variable support, URL management, Flow control

Ex: out, import, set, remove, if, choose, when
ii)Function Tags: String manipulation
iii)Formatting Tags:Message formatting, number formatting, date formatting
iv)XML Tags: flow control, transformation
v)SQL Tags: SQL support

Servlet, JSP, JSTL

Ant, Maven, Gradle - Build tools



